<h1>Billing :: Create Quotation</h1>
<h2><img src="<?php echo $root_path; ?>/gui/img/common/default/frage.gif" alt="" width=15 height=15> How to create a new quotation/bill for a person (Details)? </h2>
<p>
<span class="bold" >Note:</span> 
Care2x shows you all unpaid items of this person now. For each item you have to select an action:
<br>
<br>
<img src="<?php echo $root_path; ?>/help/en/img/en_quotation_select_tick.gif" alt="" style="float:left;" width=26 height=66>
Yes, add this item to the new bill. If you want to do this with all items click on the button "Select".
<br style="clear:both"><br/>
<img src="<?php echo $root_path; ?>/help/en/img/en_quotation_select_clock.gif" alt="" style="float:left;" width=26 height=66>
Set item on status "hold" (item will be ignored up to the next quotation). 
If you want to do this with all items click on the button "Todo".
<br style="clear:both"><br/>
<img src="<?php echo $root_path; ?>/help/en/img/en_quotation_select_cross.gif" alt="" style="float:left;" width=26 height=66>
Remove this item from the "unpaid items"-list and ignore it in the new bill.
If you want to do this with all items click on the button "Delete".
<br style="clear:both">
<br>

<span class="bold" >Step 1:</span> 
Select an action for each item.
<br>
<span class="bold" >Step 2:</span> 
If a person is unable to pay a prescription only partly adjust the dosage and price and write down a short note.
<br>
<br>
<img src="<?php echo $root_path; ?>/help/en/img/en_quotation_prescription.gif" alt="" width=448 height=45>
<br><br>
<span class="bold" >Step 3:</span> 
Click on "Calculate Total Sum" to show the total amount of money that must be payed.
<br>
<span class="bold" >Step 4:</span> 
Click on "I'm finished" if you're ready to create the new bill or "Reset Fields" to start from scratch.
</p>
